Have an unidentified dye for each duplicate dye that your characters had unlocked. Dyes can now be used across your entire account!
All of your soulbound legendary and ascended gear is being converted to account bound.

Upon entering the PvP lobby, all of your PvP armor and weapon skins from your PvP locker were transferred to your new wardrobe. For every PvP Rank that you have gained, you also received a transmutation charge. If you have other characters, enter the PvP lobby with each one to have that character's skins automatically transferred over as well. With this change, the PvP locker has been removed. Thank you again for playing PvP and using the PvP locker!
Transferring Your Equipment to Your Wardrobe

Upon entering the PvP lobby, you'll notice a new PvP-specific quick-launch bar at the top of your screen. A few of the options may seem familiar to you, but we've added something new—you can now change your runes, sigils, traits, and stat combinations entirely within your PvP Build interface. We've also added a few additional runes, sigils, and stat combinations to PvP, so be sure to check those out!

Hi! I felt it appropriate to thank you for everything you did. You're a true friend of the Soundless, and you'll always be welcome here.

Life on the isle is still difficult, but we continue to persevere, thanks in no small part to all your help. Be sure to stop by Mabon Market, just east of the island. I'm sure there's a need for someone as talented as yourself.

Thanks again!

—Eona
